<li id="cite_note-dubuisson-29"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-dubuisson_29-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-dubuisson_29-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFDubuisson2007" class="citation book">Dubuisson, Daniel (2007). <i>The Western Construction of Religion&#160;: Myths, Knowledge, and Ideology</i>. Baltimore, Md.: Johns Hopkins University Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-8018-8756-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8018-8756-7"><bdi>978-0-8018-8756-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Western+Construction+of+Religion+%3A+Myths%2C+Knowledge%2C+and+Ideology&amp;rft.place=Baltimore%2C+Md.&amp;rft.pub=Johns+Hopkins+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8018-8756-7&amp;rft.aulast=Dubuisson&amp;rft.aufirst=Daniel&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReligion" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
