<li id="cite_note-WhitefordII2008-37"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-WhitefordII2008_37-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFWhitefordTrotter_II2008" class="citation book">Whiteford, Linda M.; Trotter II, Robert T. (2008). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=ZeokAAAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA22"><i>Ethics for Anthropological Research and Practice</i></a>. Waveland Press. p.&#160;22. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-4786-1059-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-4786-1059-5"><bdi>978-1-4786-1059-5</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Ethics+for+Anthropological+Research+and+Practice&amp;rft.pages=22&amp;rft.pub=Waveland+Press&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-4786-1059-5&amp;rft.aulast=Whiteford&amp;rft.aufirst=Linda+M.&amp;rft.au=Trotter+II%2C+Robert+T.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DZeokAAAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPA22&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReligion" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
